This project was developed in HTML, CSS, PHP and JavaScript using WampServer as the local esting server and code editors including Adobe Dreamweaver and Eclipse.

To install it:
- add the folder "project" to an appropriate folder on a local or live server.
- create a database and insert the login credentials in the file "common.php" under the "includes" folder.
- use the file db.sql to populate the database with sample data.
Note: Unless the appropriate privileges have been changed, you will need to remove the SQL DROP statement to allow the data to be processed.